Rumors spread,
the site was created,

00:16:32.434 --> 00:16:35.767 position:19% line:83% align:start
posts gained attention,
soon it was popular.

00:16:35.801 --> 00:16:37.067 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's obvious.

00:16:37.100 --> 00:16:39.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
They must've used various
methods to make sure

00:16:39.868 --> 00:16:41.167 position:24% line:83% align:start
that her popularity
didn't fade.

00:16:41.200 --> 00:16:44.033 position:30% line:83% align:start
Otherwise then,
it wouldn't be possible

00:16:44.067 --> 00:16:47.067 position:13% line:83% align:start
to manifest such a monster
so quickly.

00:16:50.567 --> 00:16:54.100 position:16% line:83% align:start
We aren't limited to one
solution to solve everything.

00:16:54.133 --> 00:16:56.567 position:10% line:89% align:start
You said it yourself earlier.

00:16:56.601 --> 00:16:58.334 position:21% line:89% align:start
Divide each problem.

00:16:59.234 --> 00:17:01.634 position:16% line:83% align:start
We'll take steps to shape
the reality,

00:17:01.667 --> 00:17:03.100 position:13% line:89% align:start
the thousands of fantasies,

00:17:03.133 --> 00:17:06.000 position:13% line:83% align:start
all closer to the solution
you want to create.

00:17:06.033 --> 00:17:08.300 position:19% line:83% align:start
But until that's done,
I'll strive

00:17:08.334 --> 00:17:11.534 position:19% line:83% align:start
to determine the future
that's going to happen.

00:17:11.567 --> 00:17:12.868 position:24% line:89% align:start
But if you do that,

00:17:12.901 --> 00:17:16.834 position:7% line:83% align:start
then it means that you'll have
to die a whole bunch of times.

00:17:16.868 --> 00:17:19.501 position:33% line:83% align:start
And yesteday,
you said you would.

00:17:19.534 --> 00:17:20.601 position:30% line:89% align:start
I guess I did.

00:17:22.567 --> 00:17:23.501 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:17:32.868 --> 00:17:34.100 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:17:44.267 --> 00:17:46.701 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>She's been breaking down all</i>
 <i>the information</i>

00:17:46.734 --> 00:17:47.968 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>since yesterday,</i>

00:17:48.000 --> 00:17:50.100 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>figuring out</i>
 <i>how we can use it,</i>

00:17:50.133 --> 00:17:52.033 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and what truths</i>
 <i>we can make into lies.</i>

00:17:52.067 --> 00:17:53.434 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>What was still uncertain?</i>

00:17:53.467 --> 00:17:55.367 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>What has been</i>
 <i>absolutely verified?</i>

00:17:55.400 --> 00:17:58.300 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>She must've tried,</i>
 <i>over and over.</i>

00:17:58.334 --> 00:18:01.834 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Taking the misshapen blocks</i>
 <i>that compose our reality</i>

00:18:01.868 --> 00:18:03.834 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and determining how to</i>
 <i>create a past</i>

00:18:03.868 --> 00:18:06.167 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>that never</i>
 <i>actually existed...</i>

00:18:06.200 --> 00:18:08.234 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>Rather than</i>
 <i>seeking the truth,</i>

00:18:08.267 --> 00:18:10.634 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>she's creating</i>
 <i>alternative facts</i>

00:18:10.667 --> 00:18:12.367 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>a new, ludicrous fiction.</i>

00:18:12.400 --> 00:18:16.901 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>And with the pieces aligned,</i>
 <i>it's about to be completed.</i>

00:18:16.934 --> 00:18:19.267 position:27% line:89% align:start
[soothing music]

00:18:24.934 --> 00:18:27.267 position:27% line:89% align:start
[relishing taste]

00:18:29.567 --> 00:18:30.534 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:32.434 --> 00:18:34.934 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yes, that's sweet.

00:18:34.968 --> 00:18:36.701 position:33% line:89% align:start
You got this?

00:18:36.734 --> 00:18:37.834 position:35% line:89% align:start
I think so.

00:18:37.868 --> 00:18:40.567 position:27% line:83% align:start
I've come up with
four solutions.

00:18:40.601 --> 00:18:41.734 position:24% line:89% align:start
Now I'll use them,

00:18:41.767 --> 00:18:44.100 position:21% line:83% align:start
to round out a truth
that I want.

00:18:45.534 --> 00:18:49.367 position:13% line:83% align:start
I will defeat her tonight,
no matter what it takes.

00:18:52.767 --> 00:18:54.167 position:41% line:89% align:start
[smile]

00:18:58.234 --> 00:18:59.234 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:19:00.634 --> 00:19:02.067 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggle]

00:19:08.767 --> 00:19:11.100 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yawn]

00:19:11.734 --> 00:19:13.100 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm gonna sleep for a bit.

00:19:13.133 --> 00:19:15.234 position:7% line:89% align:start
Please wake me up before 9:00.

00:19:15.267 --> 00:19:20.734 position:7% line:83% align:start
Until then, if there's word of
Steel Lady Nanase appearing...

00:19:20.767 --> 00:19:23.467 position:10% line:89% align:start
We can just play it by ear...

00:19:30.100 --> 00:19:32.167 position:13% line:83% align:start
Let's go and get some food
for Iwanaga

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:34.167 position:24% line:83% align:start
so she can eat when
she wakes up.

00:19:34.200 --> 00:19:37.367 position:10% line:83% align:start
That said, we should probably
grab something for us too.

00:19:37.400 --> 00:19:38.601 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right.

00:19:38.634 --> 00:19:41.067 position:19% line:83% align:start
We've ordered the yokai
and monsters around the city

00:19:41.100 --> 00:19:44.501 position:27% line:83% align:start
to contact us if
they see Steel Lady Nanase.

00:19:44.534 --> 00:19:47.167 position:13% line:83% align:start
If they see her, I'll head
straight to the scene

00:19:47.200 --> 00:19:49.634 position:30% line:83% align:start
and stop Nanase
from getting away.

00:19:49.667 --> 00:19:52.501 position:21% line:83% align:start
And then, I can fight
all night if needed.

00:19:52.534 --> 00:19:56.767 position:13% line:83% align:start
Which means I can stop her
and prevent further victims.

00:19:56.801 --> 00:19:58.367 position:35% line:83% align:start
And what if
the Steel Lady escapes?

00:19:58.400 --> 00:20:01.400 position:13% line:83% align:start
We'll use our intel network
to find her again,

00:20:01.434 --> 00:20:02.567 position:24% line:89% align:start
and I'll stop her.

00:20:02.601 --> 00:20:03.701 position:21% line:89% align:start
Sounds like trouble.

00:20:03.734 --> 00:20:05.968 position:38% line:83% align:start
And yet,
it's still the best way.

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:07.434 position:21% line:89% align:start
If we hear from them,

00:20:07.467 --> 00:20:11.033 position:10% line:83% align:start
then I would like to ask you
to help me get to the scene.

00:20:11.067 --> 00:20:13.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
I've already lined up
a rental car.

00:20:13.267 --> 00:20:15.667 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sorry to get you involved
in all of this,

00:20:15.701 --> 00:20:17.167 position:10% line:89% align:start
but can I count on your help?

00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:20.901 position:7% line:83% align:start
The last thing I want to see is
any more innocent victims.

00:20:20.934 --> 00:20:23.267 position:16% line:83% align:start
Plus, I need to get over
this already.

00:20:24.601 --> 00:20:25.968 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's been a while?

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:28.467 position:16% line:83% align:start
I meant since you started
going out with her?

00:20:28.501 --> 00:20:32.133 position:7% line:83% align:start
It's been around two and a half
years since we first met.

00:20:32.167 --> 00:20:33.834 position:13% line:89% align:start
So right after we broke up?

00:20:33.868 --> 00:20:37.267 position:7% line:83% align:start
Well, no, Iwanaga only started
talking to me in May...

00:20:37.300 --> 00:20:40.701 position:27% line:83% align:start
and it's not like
we started dating immediately.

00:20:40.734 --> 00:20:42.567 position:24% line:83% align:start
I never really had
any intention

00:20:42.601 --> 00:20:43.501 position:19% line:89% align:start
of going out with her.

00:20:43.534 --> 00:20:44.534 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well, it's not like

00:20:44.567 --> 00:20:46.567 position:24% line:83% align:start
I have any right to
complain about it,

00:20:46.601 --> 00:20:48.634 position:13% line:89% align:start
but I believe you I guess.

00:20:48.667 --> 00:20:50.000 position:16% line:89% align:start
I mean, Iwanaga really is

00:20:50.033 --> 00:20:52.067 position:24% line:83% align:start
the exact opposite
of your type.

00:20:52.100 --> 00:20:55.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yeah, you're totally
right about that.

00:20:55.267 --> 00:20:58.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Yet you two seem to be</i>
 <i>doing perfectly fine.</i>

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:01.367 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Saki] I think it's good.

00:21:01.400 --> 00:21:04.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
You really shouldn't keep
chasing after Rikka anyway.

00:21:04.868 --> 00:21:06.067 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:21:09.834 --> 00:21:12.701 position:16% line:83% align:start
Saki, why'd you bring up
Rikka's name?

00:21:12.734 --> 00:21:13.968 position:33% line:89% align:start
Well, Kuro...

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:16.067 position:27% line:83% align:start
Because Rikka is
one hundred percent your type,

00:21:16.100 --> 00:21:18.067 position:10% line:89% align:start
whether you accept it or not.

00:21:19.100 --> 00:21:21.067 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Rikka Sakuragawa.</i>

00:21:21.100 --> 00:21:24.067 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Kuro's cousin, who's</i>
 <i>three years older than him.</i>

00:21:24.100 --> 00:21:26.501 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'd heard rumors that</i>
 <i>she'd passed away since,</i>

00:21:26.534 --> 00:21:29.367 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>but while Kuro and I</i>
 <i>were still dating...</i>

00:21:29.400 --> 00:21:32.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>she was a long-term patient</i>
 <i>at a university hospital.</i>

00:21:34.133 --> 00:21:37.667 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Saki] Hospitalized
for testing? For three years?

00:21:37.701 --> 00:21:39.334 position:21% line:89% align:start
Well, a lot happened.

00:21:39.367 --> 00:21:42.000 position:10% line:83% align:start
I didn't visit her that often
in high school.

00:21:42.033 --> 00:21:44.367 position:13% line:83% align:start
But the hospital's so close
to the university,

00:21:44.400 --> 00:21:46.667 position:21% line:83% align:start
I get to go visit her
more often now.

00:21:46.701 --> 00:21:48.100 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh?

00:21:48.133 --> 00:21:50.968 position:7% line:83% align:start
Then will you take me up there
to meet her sometime?

00:21:51.000 --> 00:21:53.367 position:10% line:89% align:start
Sure thing. That sounds nice.

00:22:12.901 --> 00:22:14.968 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>She was a beautiful woman.</i>

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:18.534 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>With the palest skin and</i>
 <i>a frail body.</i>

00:22:24.801 --> 00:22:28.467 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ending music]

00:23:54.501 --> 00:23:55.601 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Steel Lady Nanase</i>

00:23:55.634 --> 00:23:58.033 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>is gradually cementing</i>
 <i>her existence.</i>

00:23:58.067 --> 00:23:59.601 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Who is this Rikka Sakuragawa</i>

00:23:59.634 --> 00:24:02.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>who's controlling the future</i>
 <i>from the shadows?</i>

00:24:02.501 --> 00:24:03.601 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Next time,</i>

00:24:03.634 --> 00:24:05.367 position:16% line:89% align:start
"She Who Spins Fiction."

